product_name: Five Star Beef Natural Beef Jerky
long_description: Try the tastey Five Star Beef natural beef jerky the next time you have a taste for a delicious high-protein snack! Needs no refrigeration; can be easily taken on long trips. No preparation necessary; eat them right out of the package. Resealable bag makes keeping jerky fresh on the trail easy. Made from all-natural brisket of beef; no artificial ingredients. *Discount will be applied when you check out. Offer not valid for sale-price items ending in $._3 or $._9.
